Introduction

Yoon Seobin is a South Korean singer and model under Peace Angels Company. He made his official debut in May 2022 with the digital single, "Beautiful."

Before debuting, Yoon Seobin participated in "Produce X 101" as a trainee under JYP Entertainment. After being embroiled in bullying accusations, he left the show and was edited out. He soon left JYP and signed with Sublime Artist Agency. However, after a few activities, he left the agency and transferred to Peace Angels Company.
